.Dd $Mdocdate: July 5 2026 $
.Dt ARPCLI.CONF 5
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm arpcli.conf
.Nd arpcli configuration file
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Pa ~/.config/arpcli/conf
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Nm
file supplies connection settings for
.Xr arpcli 1 .
The file uses INI syntax with a single
.Va [api]
section.
.Pp
The configuration directory should be mode 0700 and the file mode 0600 because
it contains a secret API key.
.Sh SYNTAX
.Bl -tag -width Ds
.It Va [api]
API connection settings.
.It Va base_url
Base URL for API requests.
The default is
.Lk https://arpnetworks.com .
Trailing slashes are removed.
.It Va api_key
Bearer token created in the ARP Networks dashboard under API Keys.
Required.
.El
.Pp
Lines beginning with
.Ql #
or
.Ql ;
are comments.
Inline comments after values are not supported.
.Sh EXAMPLE
.Bd -literal -offset indent
[api]
base_url = https://arpnetworks.com
api_key = arp_live_xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx
.Ed
.Sh FILES
.Bl -tag -width Ds
.It Pa ~/.config/arpcli/conf
Default location.
.El
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr arpcli 1 ,
.Lk https://phoenix.arpnetworks.com/api/docs
